{"ID":"20260305082130-atkz9j7","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-atkz9j7","title":"引用变量","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-al1h7zm","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-al1h7zm"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 引用变量\ndate created: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 9:55:35 晚上\ndate modified: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 11:40:56 晚上\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bjqq208","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bjqq208","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是 C++ 中一个非常重要的概念，它为已存在的对象提供了一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"别名"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。引用本身不是一个对象，它只是一个已经存在的对象的另一个名称。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-68oee7j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-68oee7j","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 引用的声明与初始化"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2adn4tr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2adn4tr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bv4mjgc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bv4mjgc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Type\u0026 ref_name = variable;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2wvc1g0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2wvc1g0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心规则："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sg7kxfg","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sg7kxfg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-khfpx5k","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-khfpx5k","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-dzvfn95","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dzvfn95","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"必须在声明时初始化："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用一旦声明，就必须立即绑定到一个对象。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-z1ilniq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z1ilniq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-9o66xbj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9o66xbj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不能为"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"null"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用必须始终引用一个有效的对象。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-lh1w08v","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-lh1w08v","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-nvmhvf5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-nvmhvf5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一旦初始化不能改变指向："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用一旦绑定到一个对象，就不能再重新绑定到另一个对象。它将终生作为该对象的别名。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9f5m1j8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9f5m1j8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zv4ll0m","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zv4ll0m","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int value = 10;\nint\u0026 ref_value = value; // 声明一个 int 类型的左值引用 ref_value，并将其绑定到 value\n\nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"value: \" \u003c\u003c value \u003c\u003c std::endl;     // 输出: 10\nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"ref_value: \" \u003c\u003c ref_value \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出: 10\n\nref_value = 20; // 通过引用修改值，实际上修改的是 value\nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"value after modification: \" \u003c\u003c value \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出: 20\n\n// int\u0026 another_ref; // 错误：引用必须初始化\n// int\u0026 invalid_ref = nullptr; // 错误：引用不能为 null\n// int other_value = 30;\n// ref_value = other_value; // 错误：这不是重新绑定，而是将 other_value 的值赋给 ref_value (即 value)\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sr8lumf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sr8lumf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 引用的关键特性"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-04ttxdq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-04ttxdq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"别名："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用是其所绑定对象的另一个名称。使用引用变量，等同使用被引用的变量。对引用变量取地址，等同对被引用的变量取地址。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-c4irs2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-c4irs2l","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"没有自己的存储空间（概念上）："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 编译器通常会将引用优化为直接访问其所绑定的对象，因此引用本身通常不占用独立的内存空间（尽管在某些实现中，编译器可能会在内部将其实现为指针，但从语言层面看，它没有独立的地址）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-a19m8aq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-a19m8aq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多重引用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 对引用变量的再引用 要追溯到最原始的被引对象（不同于二级指针）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-m0r2x6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-m0r2x6a","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"安全性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 由于引用不能为 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"null"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 且不能重新绑定，它比指针更安全，避免了空指针和野指针的问题。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-nynh114","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-nynh114","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"对指针变量的引用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用指针变量时，引用的是指针变量本身，而不会引用到指针指向的地址。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-w4as0yu","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-w4as0yu","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int * x = (int *)malloc(sizeof(int));\nint * \u0026y = x;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hmeb8c4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hmeb8c4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法简洁："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 使用引用时无需解引用操作符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，语法更简洁直观。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zmspsr1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zmspsr1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 引用的类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-kefja15","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kefja15","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C++11 引入了两种主要的引用类型："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ikybjjv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ikybjjv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.1 左值引用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8cjpo7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8cjpo7x","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠Type\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"绑定对象："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 只能绑定到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"左值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（可以取地址、有名称、可以出现在赋值运算符左侧的表达式）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y19koo6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y19koo6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"左值引用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const Type\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这是一个特例，它可以绑定到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"左值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，也可以绑定到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"右值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（临时的、没有名称、不能取地址的表达式）。当绑定到右值时，⁠const 左值引用会"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"延长右值的生命周期"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，使其在引用的作用域内保持有效。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const int\u0026amp; ref_to_temp = 10;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 合法，⁠10 是右值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-90qsosc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-90qsosc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2 右值引用（C++11）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-pd92mv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pd92mv2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Type\u0026amp;\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"绑定对象："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 只能绑定到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"右值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"主要用途："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"移动语义"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完美转发"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，以提高程序性能。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":" ⁠int\u0026amp;\u0026amp; ref_to_rvalue = some_function_returning_int();"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fqn635b","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fqn635b","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 引用的主要用途"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-44a3heb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-44a3heb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.1 函数参数传递"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-eb1wtk3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-eb1wtk3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"void func(Type\u0026amp; param);"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过引用传递参数，函数内部可以修改原变量，同时避免了对象拷贝的开销。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-raym962","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-raym962","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"void func(const Type\u0026amp; param);"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用传递参数，函数内部不能修改原变量，但同样避免了对象拷贝的开销，是传递大型对象的首选方式。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-rl49o91","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-rl49o91","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.2 函数返回值"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-z0tula9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z0tula9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Type\u0026amp; func();"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数返回一个引用，允许调用者修改原变量。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2uevx6y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2uevx6y","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const Type\u0026amp; func();"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数返回一个 ⁠const 引用，调用者不能修改原变量。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zginc85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zginc85","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"许多运算符（如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠operator[]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠operator="},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）的重载函数会返回引用，以支持链式操作或允许修改。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3ya2xrz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3ya2xrz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 必须返回对一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"生命周期超出函数调用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的对象（如全局变量、静态变量、堆上分配的对象）的引用，否则会导致返回悬空引用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dlv29fo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dlv29fo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.3 迭代器"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-uxwqlwm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uxwqlwm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"STL 容器的迭代器通常通过解引用操作符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 返回对元素的引用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-tiijbs1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-tiijbs1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5 引用与指针的区别"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7mw4zhp","Type":"NodeTable","Data":"|   |   |   |\n|---|---|---|\n|特性|引用 (Reference)|指针 (Pointer)|\n|**初始化**|必须在声明时初始化，且不能为 ⁠null。|可以不初始化（为 ⁠nullptr），可以指向 ⁠null。|\n|**重新绑定**|一旦绑定，不能改变指向。|可以随时改变指向，指向不同的对象。|\n|**解引用**|直接使用引用名即可，无需解引用操作符。|需要使用 ⁠* 解引用操作符来访问所指向的值。|\n|**内存**|概念上不占用独立内存（是别名）。|占用独立内存空间，存储地址。|\n|**算术运算**|不能进行算术运算（如 ⁠ref++ 只是操作原变量）。|可以进行算术运算（如 ⁠ptr++ 移动到下一个地址）。|\n|**安全性**|更安全，避免空引用和野引用。|存在空指针和野指针的风险。|","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7mw4zhp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell"},{"Type":"NodeTableCell"},{"Type":"NodeTableCell"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特性"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"引用 (Reference)"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针 (Pointer)"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"初始化"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"必须在声明时初始化，且不能为 ⁠null。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以不初始化（为 ⁠nullptr），可以指向 ⁠null。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"重新绑定"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一旦绑定，不能改变指向。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以随时改变指向，指向不同的对象。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"解引用"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"直接使用引用名即可，无需解引用操作符。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需要使用 ⁠* 解引用操作符来访问所指向的值。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内存"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"概念上不占用独立内存（是别名）。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"占用独立内存空间，存储地址。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"算术运算"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能进行算术运算（如 ⁠ref++ 只是操作原变量）。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以进行算术运算（如 ⁠ptr++ 移动到下一个地址）。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"安全性"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更安全，避免空引用和野引用。"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"存在空指针和野指针的风险。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ph3sd1h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ph3sd1h","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6 优点"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8jmz7t8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8jmz7t8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6j0azfh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==